# MarkdownLinker  

* Search in file tree of current file, and write links to files matching criteria  

* It allows mass creation of links in markdown file  

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  

## USE TO IMPORT:  

### Names of Files & Folders  
### Links to Files & Folders  
### Folders  
### File content as code block  
### Images  

